arrested and slapped with charges of fraud, theft and money-laundering.The court
set bail conditions for Steenkamp, which included handing over her travel
documents and informing the investigating officer of any plan to leave Joburg.She is also
expected to report to the Boksburg cop shop three times a week.It was also
